and the equivalent in `@asset` - assuming that `-> None` becoming `Nothing` would cause you to change how your asset deps are defined.

```suggestion
            \mathbf{C}_g^k = \frac{1}{N_k} \sum_{i=0}^{N_k} \mathbf{r_i}
```
